verbose_text: Quantitative real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reactions (qRT-PCRs) with SYBR Green detection for PPARgamma and beta-actin gene expression were used (SYBR (R) Premix Ex TaqTM II, Takara Biotechnology [Dalian] Ltd.) on an ABI 7500 RT-PCR System (Thermo Fisher Scientific, Waltham, MA, USA).
